{"tid":1594503,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「突發」沙田站防暴再次入內捉人無人講？","createTime":"2019-09-25T14:58:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T15:04:41.000Z","uid":226156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"22af30d0c0e36d8c373f522eb6923457fc87c22d","tid":1594503,"uid":226156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:58:13.000Z","msg":"【最少兩人被捕　沙田站關閉】<br />\n<br />\n今日在沙田站有人疑因為跳閘問題引發衝突，發過百市民包圍控制室。大批警員在晚上9時半到場採取驅散行動，期間有警員衝入連城廣場並拘捕最少兩人。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵宣布，因應東鐵綫沙田站有突發情況，為確保乘客及員工的安全，沙田站暫時關閉，東鐵綫列車不停沙田站。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38750a58af9642600e7e8245ac55a5c63b58913d","tid":1594503,"uid":12662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T14:59:03.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n「置頂」 停止跳閘<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1594440\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1594440</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c29f03f8a0485c35adac383a432ddfef6dcb7c83","tid":1594503,"uid":226156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:00:39.000Z","msg":"沙田站巴士總站街坊同防暴對待緊"},{"pid":"51d59fa3d14da1780527e3f4db0ffae93ddba6e2","tid":1594503,"uid":266878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:02:28.000Z","msg":"推，要堅守每一處"},{"pid":"ab7db514d3cd51b9498491229fb1fe4e26d65333","tid":1594503,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:02:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"9c76f2f0152fb90d7577bf8331673f95a246a29e","tid":1594503,"uid":217433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:04:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}